Apostle John Mark deliver
his message ofthe apocalypse.

102
00:07:48,348 --> 00:07:50,475
[Scully] Vernon, if Sidney
was unfaithful,

103
00:07:50,583 --> 00:07:53,313
did he receive
a crown of life ?

104
00:07:53,386 --> 00:07:56,116
There are no members of the temple
named or nick named Sidney.

105
00:07:56,189 --> 00:07:58,419
