I'm Jim Jones or David Koresh.

107
00:08:03,997 --> 00:08:06,557
I don't need you
to believe or even like me.

108
00:08:06,633 --> 00:08:11,502
But just for a moment, I'd like you
to put aside your investigation...

109
00:08:11,571 --> 00:08:15,268
