that very, very soon...

111
00:08:19,212 --> 00:08:24,206
all unfaithfuls, all disbelievers,
all beasts--

112
00:08:24,317 --> 00:08:27,980
if that means me or...
this "Sidney"...

113
00:08:28,054 --> 00:08:30,249
or... you.

114
00:08:31,958 --> 00:08:35,587
All will be destroyed
by God's mighty men.

115
00:08:35,662 --> 00:08:39,723
It is what has been told
by God will happen.

116
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:44,031
