by God we must do.

117
00:08:44,103 --> 00:08:49,541
Do this and "the Lord shall
preserve you from all evil.

118
00:08:49,609 --> 00:08:52,874
" He will preserve your soul.

119
00:08:52,946 --> 00:08:56,973
"The Lord will preserve
