136
00:09:57,243 --> 00:09:59,643
A year.

137
00:09:59,712 --> 00:10:02,510
How long have you
been married to Ephesian ?

138
00:10:02,615 --> 00:10:04,606
A year.

139
00:10:04,717 --> 00:10:07,515
