146
00:10:34,514 --> 00:10:36,744
Someday.

147
00:10:38,718 --> 00:10:44,588
Vernon has to wait until God
tells him when the right soul
is ready to be reincarnated.

148
00:10:44,657 --> 00:10:49,151
