194
00:13:47,607 --> 00:13:50,542
You didn't even have the courage
to tell Skinner what you really believe:

195
00:13:50,610 --> 00:13:54,637
that Melissa Riedal is being invaded
by her past life incarnations.

196
00:13:54,747 --> 00:13:56,442
Because he wouldn't believe me.

197
00:13:56,549 --> 00:13:59,484
I don't believe that you feel
responsible for those 50 lives...

198
00:13:59,552 --> 00:14:02,020
or Melissa Riedal.

199
00:14:02,155 --> 00:14:04,680
You are only responsible
to yourself, Mulder.

200
00:14:21,140 --> 00:14:23,574
You may not want to talk about them
they may be so painful.

201
00:14:23,643 --> 00:14:26,237
You may be afraid
to remember.

202
00:14:27,847 --> 00:14:30,042
But to help the others...

203
00:14:30,149 --> 00:14:33,949
to help the children
and to help yourself,

204
00:14:34,020 --> 00:14:38,582
we're here with you to listen...
to Melissa, to Sidney,

205
00:14:38,658 --> 00:14:41,627
to whoever
may need to talk.

206
