Melissa ?

208
00:16:12,018 --> 00:16:14,282
Melissa ?

209
00:16:14,353 --> 00:16:16,287
Why you call me that ?

210
00:16:16,355 --> 00:16:19,813
- What should I call you ?
- Lily.

211
00:16:21,227 --> 00:16:21,994
Lily... were any of your friends
hurt in this room ?

212
00:16:21,994 --> 00:16:25,794
Lily... were any of your friends
