215
00:16:36,442 --> 00:16:39,070
Melissa--
Lily...

216
00:16:40,446 --> 00:16:42,607
it's okay to tell me.

217
00:16:50,323 --> 00:16:53,724
[ Sidney] Look, leave
the kid alone. Hear me ?

218
00:16:53,793 --> 00:16:56,956
She doesn't want to talk.
Right ? No way.

219
00:16:57,063 --> 00:16:59,293
I'm sending her home.

220
00:16:59,398 --> 00:17:03,732
Sidney, you can all go home.
You can all be safe, if you just
tell us where they hid the guns.

221
00:18:04,530 --> 00:18:07,158
