The weapons were placed in the bunker,

223
00:18:33,426 --> 00:18:36,054
which they had built
the night before.

224
00:18:36,128 --> 00:18:38,892
That's why they weren't
on the A.T.F. reports.

225
00:18:38,998 --> 00:18:43,332
The Federals would arrive
in the morning,just before the sun.

226
00:18:43,402 --> 00:18:47,099
Realizing the government's
might and number,

227
00:18:47,173 --> 00:18:50,267
most believed they,
indeed, would never again...

228
00:18:50,342 --> 00:18:52,469
see the light of day...

229
00:18:52,545 --> 00:18:56,242
just as they had watched their brothers
die days before on Missionary Ridge.

230
00:18:56,315 --> 00:18:58,579
We had received word...

