[ Chattering ]

442
00:37:07,005 --> 00:37:09,371
Agent Mulder,
the attorney general is furious as is.

443
00:37:09,474 --> 00:37:12,341
There's no way we're gonna
get a go-ahead for a second
move on the compound.

444
00:37:12,410 --> 00:37:14,344
Ephesian preaches
and his followers believe...

445
