488
00:39:26,811 --> 00:39:29,177
but in deed and truth.

489
00:39:29,247 --> 00:39:33,013
And here by,
we know that we are the truth.

490
00:39:35,286 --> 00:39:37,550
We shall endure.

491
00:39:39,057 --> 00:39:40,888
[Agent]
Man down! Man down !

492
00:39:42,660 --> 00:39:47,029
- Get him out of there! Cease fire !
- Hold your fire !

493
00:39:47,098 --> 00:39:50,625
[Agents Chattering]

494
00:39:50,702 --> 00:39:54,160
- Is there contact with the temple ?
- If you call that "contact."

495
00:39:54,238 --> 00:39:57,207
He should be transported
right away.

496
00:39:58,776 --> 00:40:02,439
And enter in through
the gates into the city !

497
00:40:02,513 --> 00:40:05,038
For without are dogs...

498
00:40:05,116 --> 00:40:08,847
and sorcerers...

499
00:40:08,953 --> 00:40:11,945
and who remongers...

500
00:40:12,056 --> 00:40:15,321
and murderers, idolaters.

501
00:40:20,798 --> 00:40:25,735
Whom soever loveth...

502
00:40:25,803 --> 00:40:28,738
then maketh a lie.

503
00:40:34,011 --> 00:40:36,980
[Agents Shouting]

504
00:40:38,649 --> 00:40:40,640
[Scully]
Mulder, no!

505
00:40:40,718 --> 00:40:42,652
You're dead !

506
00:40:42,754 --> 00:40:44,984
[Agent]
What is he doing ?

507
00:41:35,740 --> 00:41:37,901
[ Sobs ]

508
00:41:39,377 --> 00:41:44,212
Behold,
I am alive forever more.

509
00:43:15,573 --> 00:43:18,508
[Mulder's Voice]
At times, I almost dream.

510
00:43:20,411 --> 00:43:23,869
I, too, have spent a life
thesages' way...

511
00:43:23,948 --> 00:43:27,907
and tread once more
familiar paths.

512
00:43:27,985 --> 00:43:32,752
per chance, I've perished in an arrogant
self-reliance an age ago,

513
00:43:32,857 --> 00:43:35,587
and, in that act, a prayer
for one more chance went up...

514
00:43:35,660 --> 00:43:39,960
so earnest, so--

515
00:43:40,031 --> 00:43:42,431
Instinct with better light
let in by death...

516
00:43:42,500 --> 00:43:47,062
that life was blotted out
not so completely...

517
00:43:47,138 --> 00:43:52,474
but scattered wrecks, enough of it
to remain dim memories...

518
00:43:52,543 --> 00:43:54,738
as now...

519
00:43:54,812 --> 00:43:58,339
when seems once more...

520
00:43:58,416 --> 00:44:01,943
the goal insight again.

521
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:10,000
